---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
import { SITE } from "../site-config";
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-6" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
    <p class="sr-only">
      Hi, I'm {SITE.author.firstName}, a Master's student in Computer Science at Northeastern University (Seattle, GPA 4.0).
      I bridge technical depth and business intuition — with experience spanning software engineering,
      data analytics, and business operations at Amazon, AWS, and Huawei.
      My primary tools include Python, SQL, Java, React, and data visualization.
      Beyond coding, I enjoy hiking, traveling, and exploring new cuisines.
    </p>
    <div aria-hidden="true" class="text-sm font-light">
      <p class="text-sm font-light">
        Hi, I'm {SITE.author.firstName}, an MS Computer Science student at Northeastern University (Seattle), GPA 4.0.
      </p>
      <br />
      My primary tools of choice:
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Python, SQL, Java</li>
        <li>React, Astro</li>
        <li>Tableau, QuickSight</li>
        <li>Oracle ERP, Salesforce</li>
        <li>Data Modeling & ETL</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-sm font-light mt-2">
        Background in software engineering, business operations, and financial analytics.
      </p>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      Previously: Software Engineer Co-op at SlicPix, Business Operations Manager at AWS Shanghai,
      and Financial Analyst at Amazon Logistics. I enjoy building things that bridge technical
      and business problems.
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>
